'''Dobroč''' ({{lang-hu|Dabar}}) is a village and municipality in the [[Lučenec District]] in the [[Banská Bystrica Region]] of [[Slovakia]].

==History==
In [[history|historical records]], the [[village]] was first mentioned in 1393  (''Dobrocha'')  as belonging to [[Divín]] castle.

